text: Qhiyaamah Ayr√≥ Yallaa kee kay farmoyta Nummayse marih foocitte Qaddowtah iftah, Yallih Amri cineeh kay farmoyta dirabboyse marih foocitte dattowtah, tokkel foocitte kak dattowte marah tu-gactek ken Sahitak teemeneeniik lakal koroositteenii? Toysa isin koroositteenih Sugteenimih Sabbatah digaala tammoysa keenik iyyan
